

Verkko uses environment variable VERKKO to locate its
scripts and binaries.  It should be set so that files
  $VERKKO/Snakemake
  $VERKKO/verkko.sh
  $VERKKO/scripts/get_layout_from_mbg.py
exist.


Verkko requires several binaries to be installed in $VERKKO/bin/.
  GraphAligner     - From ...
  MBG              - From ...
  layoutToPackage  - From Canu
  utgcns           - From Canu


Sample Verkko command:
  $VERKKO/bin/verkko.sh \
    -d /assembly/my-genome/assembly-1 \
    --hifi /assembly/my-genome/hifi-reads/*.fasta.gz \
    --nano /assembly/my-genome/nanopore-reads/*.fasta \
           /assembly/my-genome/more-nano/*.fq.xz

